      "text": "Overview"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "IoHwAb module is a config project module and shall handle all variant handling and Context abstraction activties."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "With this layered approach we don't need to touch the other modules during different board bringups"
